Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait' before transitioning to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait' followed by 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum duration of 'Accepted + Wait' before any subsequent activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Maximum duration of 'Accepted + Wait' across all variants
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + Closed' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in cases where 'Completed + In Call' occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Longest duration of 'Accepted + Wait' before transitioning to any 'Completed' status
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Shortest duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in cases leading to 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in cases with more than one occurrence of 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in cases that involve 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' before or after the activity

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in the variant with the highest performance involving 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Difference in average duration between 'Accepted + Wait' and 'Accepted + In Progress' across all cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'
